7e3763c5b99d66f872de23d30c2353a3e8215539.query:
INSERT INTO notification
                  (
                    id,
                    title,
                    kind,
                    status,
                    source_id,
                    source_html_url,
                    metadata,
                    updated_at,
                    last_read_at
                  )
                VALUES
                  ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9)
                ON CONFLICT (source_id) DO UPDATE
                SET
                  title = $2,
                  kind = $3,
                  status = $4,
                  source_html_url = $6,
                  metadata = $7,
                  updated_at = $8,
                  last_read_at = $9
                RETURNING
                  id

d296e92ca52f935b64e8c8c11740fc68c35608c2.query:
SELECT
                  id,
                  title,
                  kind,
                  status,
                  source_id,
                  source_html_url,
                  metadata as "metadata: Json<GithubNotification>",
                  updated_at,
                  last_read_at
                FROM
                  notification
                WHERE
                  status = $1

e3f5a2eeccaeda8cd6d4f139c6a0be8b5f1f7986.query:
UPDATE
                  notification
                SET
                  status = $1
                WHERE
                  NOT source_id = ANY($2)
                  AND (status = 'Read' OR status = 'Unread')
                RETURNING
                  id,
                  title,
                  kind,
                  status,
                  source_id,
                  source_html_url,
                  metadata as "metadata: Json<GithubNotification>",
                  updated_at,
                  last_read_at
